Title: Mad at goa
DateModified: '2019-03-03'
DatePublished: '2019-03-03'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2019/applications/mad-at-goa
SetInCountry: India
Category: Making a local connection
AuthorName: Syali Narkhede
AuthorCountry: India
Text: I was so drunk in goa i went for party in shiva valley i enoyed alot m sheen
  i was returning home some guy stopped me n he was talking to me rudely i usy slapped
  him for two times  and left from that place  and when I return to mmy goa  hostel
  i git to know he was my neighbour i was scared but he again came to me we had talk
  and then he apologize for what he did after that both enjoyed the party.
